commit.message:
Let PEP 503 compliant pypi servers not install us to old python

This means that instead of failing to install, pip will pick an older
package version.
setup error message on obsolete python versions

drop support for Python 2.7, now requires 3.5+
main change is the removal of the set-literals option and some obsolete code dealing with old python version
